1. LOAD
   Loads the data into Pig relation.

2. STORE
   Stores the loaded data in the file system.

3. DUMP
   Used to print the data present in the relation on the console.

4. FOREACH
   Used to generate specified data transformations for column data.

5. FILTER
   Filters the data based on condition and displays it .

6. GROUP BY
   Groups the data into one or more relation.

7. ORDER BY
   Used to display the contents of the relation in sorted order(asc/desc.
  
8. DESCRIBE 
   Displays the schema of the relation.
